dmca.title: DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google
dmca.principal_name: Farmer Insurance Group - Customer NPI Data

works.description:
Farmers Insurance Group umbrella company claims representative was hosting a personal website/storage media from home where they save company data on customers and claims.  The data includes drivers license, social security number, name, phone, address, auto VIN, health records regarding claims, and other non-public inforomation (NPI).  The users was terminated for this violation of corporate policy, the site was removed, but still exists in cache search.  The URL Removal Tool does not work for us as the site does not return any 404 page not found error.  

Google cached pages via Web Search:

site:24.18.242.172

Please contact me, this is a legal matter and I represent Group Information Security and Farmers Legal Privacy Officer.

Rob Prager
+1 323-964-8638
